    <main class="page">
      <section class="hero">
        <article>
          <div class="eyebrow">Career Growth</div>
          <h1>Upskill smarter to unlock higher earning potential.</h1>
          <p class="lead">Choose the right courses, build in-demand skills, and position yourself for stronger salaries in AI, data, cloud, and digital roles.</p>
          <div class="pill-row">
            <span class="pill">AI & Automation</span>
            <span class="pill">Data Analytics</span>
            <span class="pill">Cloud & DevOps</span>
            <span class="pill">Cybersecurity</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-row">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#courses">Explore Courses</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#earnings">See Salary Impact</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <aside class="stat-grid">
          <article class="mini-card">
            <strong>+35%</strong>
            Average salary growth after targeted upskilling
          </article>
          <article class="mini-card">
            <strong>6 in 10</strong>
            Employers prefer candidates with practical digital skills
          </article>
          <article class="mini-card">
            <strong>3–6 months</strong>
            Typical time to gain employable project-ready skills
          </article>
        </aside>
      </section>

      <section id="courses">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <h2>Popular upskill courses</h2>
            <p>Short, focused learning tracks that build real job-ready value.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-3">
          <article class="car">
            <span class="tag">AI • Beginner to Intermediate</span>
            <h3>Generative AI for Work</h3>
            <p>Learn how to use AI tools for automation, content creation, research, and productivity.</p>
            <div class="meta"><span>Duration: 4 weeks</span><span class="salary">ROI: High</span></div>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <span class="tag">Data • Practical</span>
            <h3>Data Analytics Essentials</h3>
            <p>Master spreadsheets, dashboards, and data storytelling to support decisions across teams.</p>
            <div class="meta"><span>Duration: 6 weeks</span><span class="salary">ROI: Very High</span></div>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <span class="tag">Cloud • Career Growth</span>
            <h3>Cloud Fundamentals</h3>
            <p>Build a strong base in cloud platforms, deployment, and modern infrastructure concepts.</p>
            <div class="meta"><span>Duration: 5 weeks</span><span class="salary">ROI: High</span></div>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <span class="tag">Cyber • Security Focus</span>
            <h3>Cybersecurity Awareness</h3>
            <p>Understand threats, secure workflows, and protect systems in a fast-changing digital world.</p>
            <div class="meta"><span>Duration: 4 weeks</span><span class="salary">ROI: High</span></div>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <span class="tag">Digital • Marketing</span>
            <h3>Digital Marketing & Analytics</h3>
            <p>Learn campaign strategy, paid media, SEO basics, and conversion metrics to drive growth.</p>
            <div class="meta"><span>Duration: 5 weeks</span><span class="salary">ROI: Strong</span></div>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <span class="tag">Product • Business</span>
            <h3>Project & Product Skills</h3>
            <p>Improve planning, communication, and execution skills that help you stand out in tech and business roles.</p>
            <div class="meta"><span>Duration: 3 weeks</span><span class="salary">ROI: Strong</span></div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="earnings">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <h2>Earning potential by skill area</h2>
            <p>These areas often unlock stronger compensation as employers compete for modern capabilities.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-2">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>AI & Automation</h3>
            <p>Skills in automation, prompt engineering, and AI workflows are increasingly valuable across operations, marketing, and software teams.</p>
            <p class="salary">Typical pay boost: +10% to +25% depending on role and experience.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>Data Analytics</h3>
            <p>Analytical and reporting skills help professionals move into higher-responsibility roles with better pay bands.</p>
            <p class="salary">Typical pay boost: +12% to +30% for data-driven roles.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>Cloud & DevOps</h3>
            <p>Cloud literacy and automation skills open doors to infrastructure, platform, and engineering positions with strong salary growth.</p>
            <p class="salary">Typical pay boost: +15% to +35% in technical teams.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>Cybersecurity</h3>
            <p>Security knowledge is critical for business resilience and often commands premium compensation in many organizations.</p>
            <p class="salary">Typical pay boost: +18% to +40% in risk and operations roles.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="highlight-box">
        <h3>Why this matters</h3>
        <p>Upskilling is not just about learning new tools — it is about proving value, increasing your marketability, and building a stronger career path with better earnings over time.</p>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
